From: EVL infrastructure changes for SpacemiT K1
Date: Wed, 01 Apr 2026 13:06:16 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0003] evl: copy core infrastructure from EVL tree

Copy EVL-modified core kernel headers and source files from the EVL
reference tree (linux-evl) to the SpacemiT K1 tree. These are the
modifications EVL makes to vanilla kernel files to support the IRQ
pipeline (Dovetail) and EVL core.

Files modified:
  include/linux/: preempt.h, sched.h, irqflags.h, hardirq.h, etc.
  kernel/irq/: handle.c, manage.c, chip.c, etc.
  kernel/: fork.c, exit.c, context_tracking.c, etc.
---
Only in /home/lindows/work/linux-k1/include/linux/mfd: spacemit
Only in /home/lindows/work/linux-k1/include/linux/platform_data: k1x_ci_usb.h
Only in /home/lindows/work/linux-k1/include/linux/platform_data: k1x_sdhci.h
Only in /home/lindows/work/linux-k1/include/linux/: spacemit
